data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the vibrant 55+ Dell Webb Community! This meticulously maintained property offers an array of features designed to enhance your comfort and lifestyle. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the warmth of beautiful bamboo wood floors that flow throughout the home. No Carpet! Natural light floods the interior thanks to strategically placed skylights, creating an inviting and airy atmosphere. The kitchen has granite counter tops, gas cooking, and a APEC water filter system. HVAC has built in UV light air cleanser. The living room and office boast new fan fixtures, providing both functionality and style. The spacious primary bedroom includes a convenient walk-in closet, ensuring ample storage space. Outside, the property is equally impressive. An irrigation system covers both the front and back yards, maintaining lush greenery effortlessly. A charming rot iron fence encloses the property, offering privacy and security. The backyard oasis is perfect for relaxation and entertaining, featuring a pergola on the patio and a screened-in porch that overlooks a tranquil greenbelt. Xeriscaping has been added to the side yard, minimizing water usage while maximizing visual appeal. A flourishing lime tree adds a touch of freshness to the landscape. For those in need of additional storage, the garage has been equipped with extra storage solutions, keeping your belongings organized and easily accessible. Living in this community means enjoying an unparalleled array of amenities. The 28,000 sq ft amenities center offers both indoor and outdoor pools and hot tubs, providing year-round recreation options. Stay active with Bocce, Pickleball, and tennis courts, or unwind with a good book in the library. A state-of-the-art fitness center caters to all your exercise needs, while scenic walking trails invite you to explore the great outdoors! But the amenities don't stop there! With over 100 special interest groups to choose from, including Bridge, Bunco, Golf, and Garden Club, there's always something new to discover and friends to make. Don't miss your chance to experience the ultimate in active adult living. Schedule a viewing today and make this your forever home in Dell Webb Community!
